05-04 Tuscaloosa News\">{{cite news |date=1981-05-04 |title=Dr. Raymond McLain |work=[[The Tuscaloosa News]] |language=en |page=12}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"1982-04-29 NYT\">{{cite news |last1=Palmer |first1=Robert |author-link1=Robert Palmer (writer) |date=1982-04-29 |title=Bluegrass: McLain Family Gives Carnegie Hall Concert |url=https://www.nytimes.com/1982/04/29/arts/bluegrass-mclain-family-gives-carnegie-hall-concert.html |url-status=live |work=[[The New York Times]] |language=en |publisher=[[Punch Sulzberger]] |page=C22 |issn=0362-4331 |oclc=1645522 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310124532/https://www.nytimes.com/1982/04/29/arts/bluegrass-mclain-family-gives-carnegie-hall-concert.html |archive-date=2016-03-10 |access-date=2019-12-16}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"1982-07-23 Advocate-Messenger\">{{cite news |date=1982-07-23 |title=McLain Family to perform at Fort Harrod |work=[[The Advocate-Messenger]] |page=23}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"1984-09-04 Daily News\">{{cite news |date=1984-09-04 |title=7th Annual McLain Family Festival August 10\u201311 |work=[[Daily News (Kingsport)|Daily News]] |page=3}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"1985-01-06 WAPO\">{{cite news |last1=McLellan |first1=Joseph |author-link1=Joseph McLellan |date=1985-01-06 |title=Bark To Basics With P.D.Q. Bach |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/style/1985/01/06/bark-to-basics-with-pdq-bach/f509c39b-3ce2-481e-a9ae-36331e7aa2f3/ |url-status=live |work=[[The Washington Post]] |language=en |publisher=[[Donald E. Graham]] |issn=0190-8286 |oclc=2269358 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305060418/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/lifestyle/style/1985/01/06/bark-to-basics-with-pdq-bach/f509c39b-3ce2-481e-a9ae-36331e7aa2f3/ |archive-date=2016-03-05 |access-date=2019-12-16}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"1987-08-23 LAT\">{{cite news |last1=Hillinger |first1=Charles |author-link1=Charles Hillinger |date=1987-08-23 |title=Bighill, Ky., Plays Host to 6,000 Music Lovers |url=https://www.latimes.com/archives/la-xpm-1987-08-23-vw-3158-story.html |url-status=live |work=[[Los Angeles Times]] |language=en |location=[[Bighill, Kentucky]] |publisher=[[Tom Johnson (journalist)|Tom Johnson]] |issn=0458-3035 |oclc=3638237 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307104332/http://articles.latimes.com/1987-08-23/news/vw-3158_1_bluegrass-festival |archive-date=2016-03-07 |access-date=2019-12-16}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"2000-11-14 ETSU\">{{cite web |url=http://www.etsu.edu/etsu/news/20000119.htm |title=McLain Family Band to reunite for concert Saturday |date=2000-11-14 |publisher=[[East Tennessee State University]] |language=en |access-date=2019-12-16 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421165606/http://www.etsu.edu/etsu/news/20000119.htm |archive-date=2016-04-21}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"2004 Homegrown Music: CH4\">{{cite book |last1=Ledgin |first1=Stephanie P. |year=2004 |chapter=Bluegrass Bends and Blends |title=Homegrown Music: Discovering Bluegrass |language=en |location=[[Westport, Connecticut]] |publisher=[[Greenwood Publishing Group|Praeger Publishers]] |pages=37\u201352 |isbn=0-275-98115-0 |lccn=2004050964}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"2004 Homegrown Music: CH5\">{{cite book |last1=Ledgin |first1=Stephanie P. |year=2004 |chapter=Fiddling to Flatpicking |title=Homegrown Music: Discovering Bluegrass |language=en |location=[[Westport, Connecticut]] |publisher=[[Greenwood Publishing Group|Praeger Publishers]] |pages=53\u201368 |isbn=0-275-98115-0 |lccn=2004050964}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"2004 Homegrown Music: CH8\">{{cite book |last1=Ledgin |first1=Stephanie P. |year=2004 |chapter=The International Language of Bluegrass |title=Homegrown Music: Discovering Bluegrass |language=en |location=[[Westport, Connecticut]] |publisher=[[Greenwood Publishing Group|Praeger Publishers]] |pages=91\u2013100 |isbn=0-275-98115-0 |lccn=2004