-0507 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210192203/http://www.kentuckymonthly.com/culture/music/a-family-that-plays-together/ |archive-date=2019-12-10 |access-date=2020-03-16}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"2018-11-14 Kingsport Times-News\">{{cite news |last1=Scoggins |first1=Katherine |date=2018-11-14 |title=McLain Family Band celebrates 50 years |url=https://www.timesnews.net/Music/2018/11/14/McLain-Family-Band-marks-50-years-with-trio-of-local-performances.html |url-status=live |work=[[Kingsport Times-News]] |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210192207/https://www.timesnews.net/Music/2018/11/14/McLain-Family-Band-marks-50-years-with-trio-of-local-performances.html |archive-date=2019-12-10 |access-date=2019-12-27}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"2018-12-13 Herald-Dispatch\">{{cite news |last1=Halsey |first1=Derek |date=2018-12-13 |title=The McLain Family join Huntington Symphony for holiday show |url=https://www.herald-dispatch.com/features_entertainment/the-mclain-family-join-huntington-symphony-for-holiday-show/article_472ae05d-035c-5e27-bdea-667137048a5d.html |url-status=live |work=[[The Herald-Dispatch]] |language=en |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210192202/https://www.herald-dispatch.com/features_entertainment/the-mclain-family-join-huntington-symphony-for-holiday-show/article_472ae05d-035c-5e27-bdea-667137048a5d.html |archive-date=2019-12-10 |access-date=2020-01-10}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<!-- undated sources sorted alphabetically -->\n\n<ref name=\"Al, Alice and Ruth: About\">{{cite web |url=http://alaliceandruth.com/about/default.html |title=About the Band |publisher=Al, Alice and Ruth |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160429105901/http://www.alaliceandruth.com/about/default.html |archive-date=2016-04-29 |url-status=live |access-date=2016-09-14}}</ref><!-- exhausted -->\n\n<ref name=\"AllMusic: A Place of My Own: Overview\">{{cite web |url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/a-place